dcterms:description: The MNIST dataset is a large database of handwritten digits that is commonly used for training various image processing systems. In this paper, it is used as the data source for vehicles and RSUs.
dcterms:title: Mnist dataset

dcterms:description: The DRSU is a trusted dataset that is not influenced by any interference or attack, serving as a clean dataset for the RSU.
dcterms:title: DRSU (trusted dataset)
